snippet.title: Intergalactic Bubbles - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
It might not be a looker, but this doesn't prevent this game from being as addictive as its inspiration. Especially when you also have power ups thrown in the mix.

Intergalactic Bubbles (C) Hellscape Games

Steam Store Link:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/351490/Intergalactic_Bubbles/
(Also on iOS and Android)
